This stuff  never ceases to amaze me! I have my add on sweep board ready, 
but I wonder just how important is the human touch on the radio. I was 
thinking about adding a plate connected to the circuit ground that I just 
touch while recording.

I haven&#39;t heard much about those &quot;stations&quot; in other cities, and countries 
for a few years. I still get them once in a while. I think I spend way too 
much time putting boards together, and don&#39;t get time to play. This voice 
even sounds like a British accent.



Frank



